fll-live-initscripts (1.1.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll-locales: many enhancements and bugfixes
    - remove LANGUAGE default, the case construct handles that
    - allow FLL_LANG environment variable to trump all, allowing fll-locales
      to be useful for fll-installer
    - add MIRROR variable for all supported languages, do a sources.list
      substitution
    - allow lang=gr to select greek language profile
    - allow lang=si to select slovenian language profile
    - fix CD_VARIANT_PATH calculation, substitute spaces and brackets for
      underscores
    - rewrite save_locale_variables() to use a for loop that operates on a
      list of variables
    - use Etc/UTC and not UTC as fall back timezone.
  * fll-locales.default: add MIRROR variable.
  * fll-locales: split do_start() into specific parts for locales, timezone
    and sources list localisation. Add a special "localize" argument handling
    to script to allow installer to only execute what it needs -> locales
    settings.
  * fll-hwsetup: do not bother announcing sound card label, who really
    cares to know that when we can save a second or two at bootup.

